[src:relation-extraction/natural-language-processing] and typical sentences have multiple possible analyses: perhaps surprisingly, for a typical sentence there may be thousands of potential parses (most of which will seem completely nonsensical to a human).
[src:relation-extraction/natural-language-processing] What is the computational meaning of individual words in context?
