[src:relation-extraction/natural-language-processing] Sentiment analysis involves identifying and classifying the emotional tone expressed in text.
[src:relation-extraction/natural-language-processing] This technique involves analyzing text to determine whether the expressed sentiment is positive, negative, or neutral.
